# School Management API

This project provides a simple Node.js and Express.js-based RESTful API for managing school data using a MySQL database. It supports adding new schools and retrieving a list of schools sorted by proximity to a user's location.

## Features

- Add new schools with name, address, latitude, and longitude
- Get a list of schools sorted by proximity to a given latitude and longitude
- Input validation
- MySQL integration

## Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MySQL
- Postman (for API testing)

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/school-management-api.git
cd school-management-api
